# Design & UI Conventions

## Brand
- **Monzo palette**: Primary coral (#FE4B60), navy (#001E3A), teal (#007A8B), green (#4BB78F)
- **Font**: Plus Jakarta Sans
- **Tone**: Calm, financial tool, mobile-first

## Layout
- Mobile-first, one-hand usable
- Max content width: max-w-lg (512px) for calculator card
- Consistent spacing: p-4 sm:p-6 for cards

## Components
- Use shadcn-style components from `@/components/ui/*`
- Primary actions: coral background (variant="default")
- Secondary: outline or ghost
- All interactive elements must have aria-labels

## Accessibility
- No essential info by color only
- Keyboard navigable
- High contrast (foreground/background)
